<template>
  Home
</template>

<script>

import {inject, onMounted} from "vue";
import getMqttClient from "@/composables/getMqttClient";

export default {
  name: "Home",
  setup(props){
    onMounted(()=>{
      const client = inject('mqttClient')
      if (client){
        client.subscribe('test');
        client.on('message')
      }

    })
  }
}
</script>
